            "title": "Rediscovery of the “terrible hairy fly”, Mormotomyia hirsuta Austen (Diptera: Mormotomyiidae), in eastern Kenya, with notes on biology, natural history, and genetic variation of the Ukasi Hill population",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Robert S.",
                    "lastName": "Copeland"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
